com.ibasco.agql.core.transport.pool

Class DefaultPooledChannel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibasco.agql.core.transport.pool.PooledChannel
      • com.ibasco.agql.core.transport.pool.DefaultPooledChannel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.netty.channel.Channel, io.netty.channel.ChannelOutboundInvoker, io.netty.util.AttributeMap, Comparable<io.netty.channel.Channel>

    public class DefaultPooledChannel
extends PooledChannel

    A class that wraps an existing netty based Channel representing a channel that has been acquired from a NettyChannelPool.

    Note that using ChannelFuture.channel() does not return the actual PooledChannel type but the underlying Channel instance. This can be a problem when accessing a PooledChannel instance from a Collection

    Author:
    Rafael Luis Ibasco
